{"tid":1294115,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"拘捕冒警之人","createTime":"2019-07-07T17:41:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T17:45:47.000Z","uid":42252,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f5ba713a2e2512631811e89a352cae6916ae6a19","tid":1294115,"uid":42252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:41:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">未必可行</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有錯請指正 只係唔想各手足做柒事+比警_串返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n俗稱「101拘捕令」的《刑事訴訟程序條例》第101條列明，「任何人可無需手令而逮捕任何他合理地懷疑犯了可逮捕的罪行的人」，條則賦予市民作拘捕時可使用合理武力。何時可引用「101拘捕令」，關鍵在於「可逮捕的罪行」需要是可判處超過<span style=\"color: red;\">12個月</span>監禁的罪行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冒充任何的公職人員，均屬刑事罪行！根據《簡易程序治罪條例》第22條，任何人如冒充公職人員，無論是否意圖取得有價值的東西，均觸違法。一經定罪，可罰款二千元（第一級罰款）或監禁<span style=\"color: red;\">六個月</span>。<br />\n<br />\n即係冇王管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n資料：維基 頭條日報"},{"pid":"0b1592848b4d9bb91cd4072aab782c7e5f395e34","tid":1294115,"uid":42252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:41:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9dfdd763bd69d61c3390aa4df606b2f3fc40a0b7","tid":1294115,"uid":42252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:41:36.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"3a530c8bb32038f869dd95dcb2a83c2d5a728085","tid":1294115,"uid":42252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:41:54.000Z","msg":"唔解鎖"},{"pid":"a391615a13f5afc018b9fc87510f04243a50e1ae","tid":1294115,"uid":42252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:42:06.000Z","msg":"我要見律師"},{"pid":"4162b0a956424fefcc5f0c092f99df89a45383e7","tid":1294115,"uid":42252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:42:22.000Z","msg":"我要去醫院！"},{"pid":"55025c10b526c9ffd4f07279bf3e21f70545d35d","tid":1294115,"uid":42252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:43:04.000Z","msg